Summaries.eng: On the ancient sword field continent, there are ten magic swords and five major families. Lu Yang, one of the five major families, a descendant of the Lu family, awakens the magic sword "Peach God Sword" at a time of crisis to avoid chasing and killing. , Practice hard, avenge the mother, search for the truth, fight and mediate among the big family forces, and finally dominate the world with ten swords and seek the sword domain continent.
